videoDetails.Title: War Thunder: How to Not Suck at Ground Realistic Guide
videoDetails.Description:
SOUP SQUAAAD!!!!!! Big Soup coming at ya with another guide. This is not only my first ground rb guide, but also video. Do not expect too many of these (lol), but figured at least one was due! I wanna improve more before I start making more videos on ground. Otherwise, enjoy, and please- make sure you learn from my commentary, and not my gameplay! Like I said, improvements are still to be made.

I'm sure there's plenty of great tips I missed in the video, please, feel free to drop any advice you might have in the comments! If you're new, pay attention to the video, read the comments, and fix those skill issues :)

Last thing- SQUADRON HAS BEEN MADE!!!! If you're interested in joining, please do send in an application! The tag is =Nimbo= (=Soup= was taken, of course). The only requirement is 5 matches in any realistic battles. We've got plenty of space, and we'd love to have you in!
